<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢٤١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4670">عُمَرُ بْنُ حَفْصِ بْنِ غِيَاثٍ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1556">أَبِي </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2809">شَقِيقٌ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدَ اللهِ </a>قَالَ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَسَلَّمَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا تُبَاشِرِ الْمَرْأَةُ الْمَرْأَةَ فَتَنْعَتَهَا لِزَوْجِهَا كَأَنَّهُ يَنْظُرُ إِلَيْهَا.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>